changeLog:
1.0(Features)
•View all projects together under specified directory,
•Easy project management (Rename, delete or open in AIDE),
•View all components of a project together (Activity, Permission, Dependency, Service etc.),
•View project icon,
•Create new Activity, Fargment, Service, Broadcast receiver, Content provider or add more permission and dependency (Androidx or Support Library),
•View codes with color highlighting and multiple theme,
•Vector Asset preview (has limitations),
•View all text files and image files,
•Font preview is also available,
•6 project tamplates & easy way to create project,
•6000+ Vector Asset to import in your project,
•Adding new files from storage,
•No ads.
and many more...
